==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Weather station
<hw>Weather station</hw>. <fld>(Meteor.)</fld> <def>A station for taking
meteorological observations, making weather forecasts, or disseminating
such information. Such stations are of the <colf>first order</colf> when
they make observations of all the important elements either hourly or by
self-registering instruments; of the <colf>second order</colf> when only
important observations are taken; of the <colf>third order</colf> when
simpler work is done, as to record rainfall and maximum and minimum
temperatures.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Weatherwise</ent>⟦br⟧
